msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Creference%5Csemantic-mediation-architecture.md:3
msgid ""
"This page documents the reference architecture for semantic mediation "
"between business domain models and citizen-centric vocabularies. The CPSV "
"Editor is the authoring tool that produces artefacts for the semantic "
"mediation layer."
msgstr ""

